body:
Criminal Minds AU

Freedom from Yesterday (Jikook, VHope…)

Word reaches the FBI that a person has escaped from the hands of a serial killer who Min Yoongi and the rest of BAU have been chasing for years. Yoongi and the others, including golden child Jeon Jungkook, hurry in to protect and question him for details in order to track the murderer down once and for all.

Park Jimin is different from what Jungkook was expecting, though. He needs to be saved from more than a killer, but will he let anyone help him?

64/? Jacobs is guilty and Jimin is getting better.
